<p><strong>Name:</strong> Charles █. &quot;Waterfire&quot; ██████</p>
<p><strong>Occupation:</strong> Structural/Mechanical Engineer</p>
<p><strong>Security Clearance:</strong> 4</p>
<p><strong>Notes:</strong> Born in Arlington, Texas in 19██, Researcher Waterfire joined the Foundation in 20██. He is currently stationed in Site-101, and specializes in accident reconstruction. He has been noted to be very casual and outgoing among close colleagues, but quiet among personnel he is unfamiliar with.</p>
<p>Waterfire has been known to keep a Rubik's Cube type puzzle on his person at all times. He has regularly produced abstract drawings following his exposure to [REDACTED] (see photo).</p>
